When i went to see what was the matter she was just mad that my sister put her in her chair thing so my sister could feed her. That was not a very good start for a day.Lol. We have to go because we're in my cousin's wedding and she don't want us to have tan lines from out bathing suits. So me n my sister take turns tanning because we had the baby. And of course my sister decided that she had to go first and just kinda leave me in the car with the baby. After like two minutes the baby started screaming which definately sucked.
